Research Article
Mechanism of MicroRNA-Target Interaction: Molecular Dynamics Simulations and Thermodynamics Analysis

    Yonghua Wang ,

    * E-mail: yh_wang@nwsuaf.edu.cn

    Affiliation Center of Bioinformatics, Northwest A&F University, Yangling, Shaanxi, China
    ⨯
    Yan Li,

    Affiliation School of Chemical Engineering, Dalian University of Technology, Dalian, Liaoning, China
