Mechanism of MicroRNA-Target Interaction: Molecular Dynamics Simulations and Thermodynamics Analysis

    Yonghua Wang, 
    Yan Li, 
    Zhi Ma, 
    Wei Yang, 
    Chunzhi Ai

PLOS
x

    Published: July 29, 2010
    https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pcbi.1000866

    Article
